questions.prompt:
What is printed for `cmd = "quit"`?

```js
switch (cmd) {
  case "start":
    console.log("Starting");
    break;
  case "quit":
    console.log("Goodbye");
    break;
  default:
    console.log("Unknown command");
}
```

What is printed for `option = 2`?

```js
switch (option) {
  case 1: console.log("Add"); break;
  case 2: console.log("Remove"); break;
  case 3: console.log("List"); break;
  default: console.log("Invalid");
}
```

For `code = "1"`, which case runs?

```js
switch (code) {
  case 1: console.log("number"); break;
  case "1": console.log("string"); break;
}
```
